### Inventory Service API Tests

### 1. Create Vehicle
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "brand": "Maruti Suzuki",
  "model": "Swift",
  "year": 2020,
  "fuelType": "PETROL",
  "basePrice": 550000,
  "odometer": 25000,
  "color": "Red",
  "registrationNumber": "MH12AB1234",
  "registrationState": "Maharashtra",
  "rtoCode": "MH12",
  "ownershipType": "FIRST",
  "transmission": "MANUAL",
  "description": "Well maintained Swift in excellent condition",
  "features": "ABS, Airbags, Power Steering, AC",
  "city": "Mumbai",
  "state": "Maharashtra",
  "pincode": "400001",
  "insuranceExpiryDate": "2025-12-31"
}

### 2. Get Vehicle by ID
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles/1

### 3. Get All Vehicles
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles?status=AVAILABLE&page=0&size=20

### 4. Get Vehicles by Seller
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles/seller/1

### 5. Update Vehicle
PUT http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brand": "Maruti Suzuki",
  "model": "Swift VXI",
  "year": 2020,
  "fuelType": "PETROL",
  "basePrice": 540000,
  "odometer": 26000,
  "color": "Red",
  "transmission": "MANUAL",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "city": "Mumbai",
  "state": "Maharashtra"
}

### 6. Publish Vehicle
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles/1/publish

### 7. Add Vehicle Image
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles/1/images?imageUrl=https://example.com/car1.jpg&imageType=EXTERIOR&isPrimary=true

### 8. Get Vehicle Images
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles/1/images

### 9. Delete Vehicle Image
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles/1/images/1

### 10. Create Inspection
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles/1/inspections
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "inspectionDate": "2024-01-15",
  "inspectorName": "John Doe",
  "overallScore": 85,
  "engineScore": 90,
  "transmissionScore": 85,
  "suspensionScore": 80,
  "brakesScore": 88,
  "electricalScore": 92,
  "bodyScore": 75,
  "interiorScore": 82,
  "notes": "Vehicle is in good condition overall",
  "recommendations": "Minor body work recommended"
}

### 11. Get All Inspections
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles/1/inspections

### 12. Get Latest Inspection
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles/1/inspections/latest

### 13. Delete Vehicle
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/v1/vehicles/1
